=head1 DESCRIPTION

Settings that Image Builder uses to configure the ECR repository and
the output container images that Amazon Inspector scans.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ContainerTags => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Tags for Image Builder to apply to the output container image that
Amazon Inspector scans. Tags can help you identify and manage your
scanned images.


=head2 RepositoryName => Str

The name of the container repository that Amazon Inspector scans to
identify findings for your container images. The name includes the path
for the repository location. If you donE<rsquo>t provide this
information, Image Builder creates a repository in your account named
C<image-builder-image-scanning-repository> for vulnerability scans of
your output container images.



